<section id="about" class="section about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <h2 class="section-title">An open codebase and incubator for student developers</h2>
        <p class="about-desc">
          We build tools that make campus enlistment, navigation, and administrative simulator processes smoother. Each of our tools is entirely open source, client-side, and designed to respect student privacy.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          uplb.tools also functions as a structured training sandbox. Student contributors collaborate via GitHub pull requests, learning software engineering fundamentals, design workflows, and release cycles.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-principles">
        <div class="principle-item">
          <h4>01 / Utility Driven</h4>
          <p>We build to solve specific friction points in registration, schedule planning, and grading trackers.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="principle-item">
          <h4>02 / Educational Sandbox</h4>
          <p>We bridge the gap between academic theory and real-world development cycles using peer code reviews.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="principle-item">
          <h4>03 / Zero Tracking</h4>
          <p>No analytics engines, zero student tracking scripts, and no server-side databases.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  
  .about-desc {
    font-size: 0.925rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-zinc-400);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .about-principles {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .principle-item {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border-zinc);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .principle-item h4 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-zinc-50);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .principle-item p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-zinc-400);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
